Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:13.63,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:18.88,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:24.45,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:27.72,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,从远方传来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.49,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,心为之而动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:34.49,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:42.25,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,这悲伤的预感将是否成真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:47.74,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,未曾知晓的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:55.27,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:24:00.52,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:06.96,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,梦中迷惘 而充满自由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:12.51,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,轻声许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:18.99,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,好想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:27.41,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,相视而笑
